      "summary": "\"Girl Like Me\" is a song by English singer-songwriter and producer, PinkPantheress. It was originally an unreleased song and was later included on her second mixtape \"Fancy That\".\n\nThe song samples “Romeo” by English artist Basement Jaxx featuring Kele Le Roc. According to an interview with Mixmag, “Romeo” is her favorite sample. <a href=\"http://www.last.fm/music/PinkPantheress/_/Girl+Like+Me\">Read more on Last.fm</a>.",
